N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1211.53 - Class C explosives

State Regulations

No vehicle shall enter either a tunnel, the George

Washington Bridge Lower Level or George Washington Bridge Expressway if its
load includes any Class C explosives except small-arms ammunition tear gas
cartridges not in excess of 10 pounds gross weight, or trick matches not in
excess of 2000 pounds gross weight, or other Class C explosives for which
independent provision is made in the following sections 1211.54 to
1211.59
inclusive. Notes
